            <p>{{t "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, LINGOLINQ LLC SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUES, WHETHER INCURRED DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES, RESULTING FROM (A) YOUR ACCESS TO OR USE OF OR INABILITY TO ACCESS OR USE THE SERVICE; (B) ANY UNAUTHORIZED ACCESS TO OR USE OF OUR SECURE SERVERS AND/OR ANY PERSONAL INFORMATION STORED THEREIN." key="terms_liability"}}</p>
            <p>{{t "IN NO EVENT SHALL LINGOLINQ'S TOTAL CUMULATIVE LIABILITY TO YOU FOR ANY AND ALL CLAIMS ARISING OUT OF OR RELATING TO THIS AGREEMENT EXCEED THE GREATER OF ONE HUNDRED U.S. DOLLARS ($100.00) OR THE TOTAL AMOUNT YOU PAID TO LINGOLINQ FOR THE SERVICE IN THE TWELVE (12) MONTHS IMMEDIATELY PRECEDING THE INCIDENT GIVING RISE TO THE CLAIM." key="terms_liability_cap"}}</p>

            <h3>{{t "2. Indemnification" key="terms_indemnification_heading"}}</h3>
            <p><strong>{{t "General Indemnification:" key="terms_indemnification_general_heading"}}</strong> {{t "To the fullest extent permitted by law, you agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless LingoLinq and its team from any claims, liabilities, damages, or legal costs (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising from:" key="terms_indemnification_general"}}</p>
