            <p>{{t "We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time, with or without cause, if you violate these Terms." key="terms_termination_1"}}</p>
            <p>{{t "You may terminate your account at any time via your account settings. If you terminate your account, you will have a 10-day grace period to recover your data before it is permanently deleted, as outlined in our Privacy Policy." key="terms_termination_2"}}</p>

            <h3>{{t "Contact Us" key="terms_contact_heading"}}</h3>
